description: The ever-so-talented team behind the ever-so-beauteous Pico House is comprised of an eclectic group of new and familiar friends who, after building impressive respective careers in the culinary and arts industries, finally united in order to serve LA some nutritious deliciousness.They’re bringing out bowls of their signature blend of six different whole grains, which are sure to fill you up without ever weighing you down. Then they pile on their succulent selection of richly flavorful meats, veggies, house-made pickles, and fresh herbs. For a complete meal that nourishes your body, appetite, creativity, and soul, be sure to keep a keen eye out for Pico House.
name: Pico House
